                <name lang='en'>Hospitalized Patients With and Without Hemodialysis Have Markedly Different Vancomycin Pharmacokinetics: A Population Pharmacokinetic Model-Based Analysis</name>
            </studyName>
            <studyAuthors>Vineet Goti, Ayyappa Chaturvedula, Michael J. Fossler, Steve Mok and Jesse T. Jacob</studyAuthors>
